<header class="text-center">
  <h3>Welcome aboard!</h3>

  {{#if isCustomShop}}
    <h4 class="subheader">You are almost done...</h4>
  {{else}}
    <h4 class="subheader">You're done. There are no additional installation steps, we have done everything for you!</h4>
  {{/if}}
</header>

{{#if isCustomShop}}
  <article class="panel">
    <h4 class="subheader">There is one more thing to do</h4>

    <p>To start tracking your metrics, we need you to install our javascript tracker code to every page of your shop.</p>

    <code>
    <p><pre>&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;{{trackerScriptUrl}}&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre></p>
    </code>

    <p>The following script tracks all your successful orders. You should add it to every order complete page, passing the parameters bellow:</p>

    <code>
      <p><pre>
var _shopstream = _shopstream || [];

_shopstream.push(['addOrder',
  "Order ID", // order ID, required
  20.02, // order total, required
  "email@customer.com", // customer email, required
  "first", // customer first name, optional
  "last" // customer last name, optional
]);
_shopstream.push(['addItem',
  "SOME123SKU", // item SKU, required
  "Title", // item name, required
  10.01, // item price, required
  2 // item quantity, required
]);
_shopstream.push(['trackOrder']);
      </pre></p>
    </code>

    <h4 class="subheader">Not a developer?</h4>
		<p> Send these instructions to your developer's email address! </p>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="six columns">
        <div class="row collapse">
          <div class="seven columns">
            {{view Ember.TextField valueBinding="controller.developerEmail" placeholder="your developer's email"}}
          </div>
          <div class="five columns">
            <button {{action sendInstructions target="controller"}} {{bindAttr disabled="controller.isInvalidOrSentInstructions"}} class="postfix button expand">
              {{#if sentInstructions}}Instructions sent{{else}}Send instructions{{/if}}
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
{{/if}}

<section class="text-center">
  <a {{action goToDashboard}} class="large success button radius">
    Take me to the dashboard!
  </a>
</section>
